'''尤馬''' （{{lang-en|Yuma}}；莫哈維語：Kwichaan Nyava<ref>Munro, P et al. ''A Mojave Dictionary''. Los Angeles: UCLA, 1992.</ref>）是[[美國|美國]][[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]的一座城市，位於該州西南部、[[希拉河|希拉河]]與[[科羅拉多河|科羅拉多河]]匯合處以西，鄰近[[加州|加州]]和[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]。是[[尤馬縣_(亞利桑那州)|尤馬縣]]縣治。{{GR|6}}2000年人口77,515人，2005年人口84,688人。<ref name=popest2>{{cite web | date = 2006年6月21日 | url = http://www.census.gov/popest/cities/tables/SUB-EST2005-04-04.csv | title = Annual Estimates of the Population for All Incorporated Places in Arizona | format = [[Csv|CSV]] | work = 2005 Population Estimates | publisher = U.S. Census Bureau, Population Division | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | archive-url = http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20090710125333/http%3A//www%2Ecensus%2Egov/popest/cities/tables/SUB%2DEST2005%2D04%2D04%2Ecsv | archive-date = 2009年7月10日 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

==氣候==
尤馬擁有[[亞熱帶|亞熱帶]][[沙漠氣候|沙漠氣候]]，其夏季非常炎熱，冬季較為溫暖，其溫度普遍較低。尤馬是美國最炎熱的城市，一年平均錄得175日溫度酷熱，其溫度最高超過{{convert|90|°F|0}}。<ref>{{cite web | title = Mean Number of Days Maximum Temperature 90 Deg. F or Higher | work = Comparative Climatic Data for the United States Through 2012 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration: U.S. Dept. of Commerce | date = 2013 | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/data/ccd-data/mxge9012.txt | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131106025131/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/data/ccd-data/mxge9012.txt | archivedate = 2013-11-06 }}</ref> 

